ning doubts about the 1E 1740.7-2942 Galactic nature. To our knowledge,\nthis microquasar is the second whose jet precession ephemeris become available\nafter SS433. This kind of information is relevant to the physics of compact\nobjects, since the genesis of the precession phenomenon occurs very close to\nthe interplay region between the accretion disk and the compact object in the\nsystem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2015 18:33:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2015 09:52:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-16"}
