redicted in\nFermi acceleration. We also find that the bulk flow can carry a significant\namount of energy during the simulations. We discuss the implication of this\nstudy in the context of Poynting-flux dominated jets and pulsar winds\nespecially the applications for explaining the nonthermal high-energy\nemissions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2015 18:56:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2016 09:26:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
