eories of certain 3d long-range entangled phases, completing our\nunderstanding of general anomalous SETs in 2 dimensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2015 21:00:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2016 19:41:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
